sc_cat_item.description:
Service Overview: Our Digital Prototype Accelerator equips organizations with rapid, customizable digital product prototypes that deliver public sector services. Designed to advance from concept to prototype in just 15 minutes, our service streamlines the development process, enabling public sector organizations to focus on refinement and deployment.

Product Offerings:

  Manage Licenses and Permits:

  • Features: Request form, permit request storage, agent interface, and workflows.
  • Benefits: Streamlines processing, reduces administrative burden, and improves service delivery.

  Public Sector Service Request Management:

  • Features: Request form, service request storage, agent interface, and automated processing workflows.
  • Benefits: Enhances efficiency in handling and fulfilling general public sector service requests.

  Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Requests:

  • Features: Request form, FOIA request storage, agent interface, and request processing workflows.
  •  Benefits: Simplifies management and response to FOIA requests and ensures compliance and access.

  Health and Human Services (HHS) Program Support Desk:

  • Features: Help request form, HHS request storage, agent interface, specialized workflows.
  • Requests include Incident submission, case submission, change suggestion, and knowledge base support.
  • Benefits: Provides a robust support structure for HHS service consumers, employees, and contractors.

Key Advantages:

  1. Quick Setup: From initiation to prototype in 15 minutes.
  2. Customization: Flexible solutions adaptable to specific agency needs.
  3. Integration Ready: Designed for easy integration with existing IT infrastructures.
  4. Secure and Compliant: Meets stringent government security and compliance standards.
